      "message": "In the BUILD.gn, file, you should declare a dependency on testing in order to do this, or I bet you’ll break Chromium’s DEPS checker.\n\nBut you can’t declare a dependency on testing directly, because we don’t really have testing available at the same path in Crashpad as it is in Chromium.\n\nSo what you’ll need to do is add a group(\"testing\") to third_party/mini_chromium/BUILD.gn, and redirect things to testing in the proper location depending on the configuration, just as we do for base. (Because we have the same problem for base).",
